text: I grew up in Ruidoso, NM next to the Mescalero Apache Indian Reservation, home to 2,800 members of the Mescalero, Chiricahua, and Lipan bands of Apaches. On this #IndigenousPeoplesDay, I honor them and the other 1000+ Native American tribes for their contributions to our country.
